            the arrow graphic on the left hand side, then select <emphasis
            role="bold">Despray</emphasis> from the pop-up menu.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Check the <emphasis role="bold">Source</emphasis>
            information that is already filled in.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Provide <emphasis role="bold">Destination</emphasis>
            information.</para>

